            <title>支付寶系統錯誤自動 8 折，螞蟻：不會追收差額、提防退款詐騙短訊</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/17/alipay-accidentally-20-percent-off/life-tech/epayment/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=alipay-accidentally-20-percent-off</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/17/alipay-accidentally-20-percent-off/life-tech/epayment/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 07:00:37 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[電子支付]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Alipay]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[支付寶]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[螞蟻金融]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1287527</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>支付寶昨日（16 日）因技術問題，導致部分訂單價格自動調整為 8 折，並顯示「政府補貼」訊息。事件引致系統出現大量交易金額異常，針對今次事故，螞蟻集團已公開承諾承擔全責，並明確表示不會向用戶追討折扣差額。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287529" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/e2978da9203f958c9992-520x580.jpg" alt="" width="520" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/e2978da9203f958c9992-520x580.jpg 520w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/e2978da9203f958c9992.jpg 807w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 520px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲漏洞發生期間出現「政府補貼」訊息，圖片來源：<a href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/roll/2025-01-17/doc-ineffpzn3580049.shtml">新浪財經</a></p><p>昨日（17 日）下午 2 點 40 至 45 分期間，有用戶使用支付寶交易時，因系統錯誤，支付金額自動 8 折，並顯示「政府補貼」。經調查問題源於伺服器調整期間技術漏洞。儘管技術團隊迅速修復系統，但已波及不少用戶。支付寶發言人表示相關損失將由平台全數承擔，用戶毋須為此擔憂。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287530" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/1d0173c4043c53414f36-425x580.jpg" alt="" width="425" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/1d0173c4043c53414f36-425x580.jpg 425w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/1d0173c4043c53414f36.jpg 660w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 425px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲支付時顯示「政府補貼」訊息，圖片來源：<a href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/roll/2025-01-17/doc-ineffpzn3580049.shtml">新浪財經</a></p><p>支付寶亦發表聲明，澄清所有「追回資金」的短訊均為詐騙，強調不會追回漏洞發生期間損失的金額，並呼籲市民提防受騙。聲明澄清指：「支付寶官方沒有發送任何資金追回短信，如果你收到了下圖短信，千萬不要點，以免上當受騙，也請大家幫忙相互轉告。」</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287531" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011720910-628x580.jpg" alt="" width="628" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011720910-628x580.jpg 628w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011720910.jpg 635w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 628px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲偽冒支付寶的詐騙短訊，圖片來源：<a href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/roll/2025-01-17/doc-ineffpzn3580049.shtml">新浪財經</a></p><p>支付寶透露，是次事故是配合常規營銷活動時誤設營銷模板，技術人員誤值優惠額及類型，並再次重申不會向用戶追回任何已發出的優惠。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287528" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/a3ca6f372f6f5a107693-220x580.jpg" alt="" width="220" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/a3ca6f372f6f5a107693-220x580.jpg 220w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/a3ca6f372f6f5a107693.jpg 342w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 220px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/roll/2025-01-17/doc-ineffpzn3580049.shtml">新浪財經</a></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/roll/2025-01-17/doc-ineffpzn3580049.shtml">新浪財經</a>、<a href="https://www.sohu.com/a/849918633_116062?scm=thor.521_14-200000.0.0.&amp;spm=smpc.home.it-news11.6.17370756000165oXoZw5_1467&amp;_trans_=060008_lym">搜狐</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 傾傾科技背後黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
