            <title>LG 發佈第四代 OLED 面板，亮度提升 33% 可達 4000 尼特</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/17/lg-announce-4th-gen-oled-panel/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=lg-announce-4th-gen-oled-panel</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/17/lg-announce-4th-gen-oled-panel/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Edward]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 03:00:16 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[4th Gen]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[lg]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[OLED]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1287464</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在今年的 CES，一向習慣推出新技術的 LG 卻沒有甚麼大動作，正當大家以為 LG 在顯示發展未有甚麼新搞作的時候，近日就正式宣佈推出他們的第四代 OLED 面板，當中採用了全新的 Primary RGB Tandem 架構，據指亮度比上代，即第三代 OLED 面板提升了 33%，即最高可達 4000 尼特。另外亦有不少新功能展現，想了解更多就要瀏覽內文了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287469" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_008-694x360.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="360" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_008-694x360.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_008.jpg 1013w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>LG 在新聞稿中發佈最新第四代的 OLED 面板，它採用了全新的 Primary RGB Tandem 架構，據 LG 技術文件表示，相比第三代採用藍-黃-藍的三層架構，第四代 OLED 的 Primary RGB Tandem 架構將會設為四層，分別為紅-藍-綠-藍架構，據官方指這個改動不但可以有效提升面板亮度，更可以令色準表現更佳。而更難得的是新面板不但令峯值亮度提升達 33%，同時功耗亦相應減低 20%，換言之在使用時將會更為省電。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287467" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_003-694x288.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="288" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_003-694x288.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_003.jpg 1198w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>此外，面板表面亦加入了全新的 Ultra anti-reflection 技術，據指可將高達 99% 的光線擋走，從而達到防反光的效果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287468" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_015-694x283.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="283" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_015-694x283.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_015.jpg 1161w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>LG 亦表示第四代 OLED 面板的 DCI-P3 色域將達到 99.5%，而且在光或暗的環境，均可將真實的黑位呈現出來，令大家睇戲時不用拉窗簾，都可以有十分不錯的觀賞效果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287470" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_004-694x290.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="290" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_004-694x290.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_004.jpg 1199w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287471" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_005-694x288.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="288" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_005-694x288.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_005.jpg 1199w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>官方亦指出這塊第四代 OLED 面板將會應用在 48 吋至 83 吋的五個尺寸電視上，相信下半年大家應該會看到相關產品現身吧？</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287472" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_007-694x337.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="337" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_007-694x337.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_007.jpg 1116w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.lgdisplay.com/eng/company/media-center/latest-news?contentId=5372">LG Display</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
